###Block: Gibbering Mouther abilities
# Ability Name		Unique Key							Category of Ability		Type								Define					Description																																											Modify VAR									Source Page		Aspects							Description of the Benefits
Amorphous			KEY:Amorphous ~ Gibbering Mouther			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.Defensive							DESC:Your body is malleable and shapeless.																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.153									BENEFIT:Your body is malleable and shapeless. You are immune to precision damage (like sneak attacks) and critical hits, and can move through an area as small as one-quarter of your space without squeezing or one eighth of your space when squeezing.
Blood Drain			KEY:Blood Drain ~ Gibbering Mouther			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary.AttackOption							DESC:On a successful grapple check after grabbing, your mouths automatically deal 1d4 points of bite damage and 1 point of Constitution damage as you drain your victim's blood.																									SOURCEPAGE:p.153									BENEFIT:On a successful grapple check after grabbing, several of your mouths attach to its target. Each round you maintain your grapple, your mouths automatically deal 1d4 points of bite damage and 1 point of Constitution damage as you drain your victim's blood.
Engulf			KEY:Engulf ~ Gibbering Mouther			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary.AttackOption							DESC:This ability functions as swallow whole, except for the changes noted.																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.153									BENEFIT:This ability functions as swallow whole, except for the following changes. An engulfed creature is trapped in the gibbering mouther's body, where several of its mouths continue to feed and drain blood. A gibbering mouther can engulf only one foe of its size or smaller at a time. If an engulfed creature cuts its way free (the mouther's damage reduction still applies to those inside), the mouther simply flows together again and can still use its engulf attack.
Gibbering			KEY:Gibbering ~ Gibbering Mouther			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary.AttackOption	DEFINE:GibberingDC|10+(HD/2)+CON	DESC:As a free action, a gibbering mouther can emit a cacophony of maddening sound.																															BONUS:VAR|GibberingDC|2|PREFEAT:1,Ability Focus (Gibbering)	SOURCEPAGE:p.153	ASPECT:Ability Benefit|(DC %1)|GibberingDC	BENEFIT:As a free action, a gibbering mouther can emit a cacophony of maddening sound. All creatures other than gibbering mouthers within 60 feet must succeed on a DC %1 Will save or be confused for 1 round. This is a mind affecting compulsion insanity effect. A creature that saves cannot be affected by the same mouther's gibbering for 24 hours.|GibberingDC
Grab				KEY:Grab ~ Gibbering Mouther				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary.AttackOption							DESC:If a gibbering mouther hits with the indicated attack, it deals normal damage and can attempt to start a grapple as a free action without provoking an attack of opportunity. A gibbering mouther can use its grab attack against a foe of up to Medium size.	BONUS:VAR|CMB_Grapple|4							SOURCEPAGE:p.301									BENEFIT:If a gibbering mouther hits with the indicated attack, it deals normal damage and can attempt to start a grapple as a free action without provoking an attack of opportunity. A gibbering mouther can use its grab attack against a foe of up to Medium size. A gibbering mouther has the option to conduct the grapple normally, or simply use the part of its body it used in the grab to hold the opponent. If it chooses to do the latter, it takes a -20 penalty on its CMB check to make and maintain the grapple, but does not gain the grappled condition itself. A successful hold does not deal any extra damage. Each successful grapple check you make during successive rounds automatically deals the damage indicated for the attack that established the hold. A gibbering mouther receives a +4 bonus on combat maneuver checks made to start and maintain a grapple.
Ground Manipulation	KEY:Ground Manipulation ~ Gibbering Mouther	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural.AttackOption							DESC:At will as a standard action, a gibbering mouther can cause stone and earth under its body to grow soft and muddy.																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.153									BENEFIT:At will as a standard action, a gibbering mouther can cause stone and earth under its body to grow soft and muddy. The ground remains muddy for 1 minute after the mouther moves off of the location. A gibbering mouther can move through these areas with ease, but other creatures treat them as difficult terrain.
Spittle			KEY:Spittle ~ Gibbering Mouther			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary.AttackOption	DEFINE:SpittleDC|10+(HD/2)+CON	DESC:Each round as a free action, a gibbering mouther can emit a stream of acidic spittle at one target within 30 feet.																									BONUS:VAR|SpittleDC|2|PREFEAT:1,Ability Focus (Spittle)	SOURCEPAGE:p.153	ASPECT:Ability Benefit|(+6 ranged touch)		BENEFIT:Each round as a free action, a gibbering mouther can emit a stream of acidic spittle at one target within 30 feet. On a successful attack, the target is blinded for 1d4 rounds unless he succeeds on a DC %1 Fortitude save.|SpittleDC

